  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create an earthen dragon of a certain size, whose Perform Requirements, Range, Area, Cost and damage change based on the dragon's size. In all cases, the damage is dealt to all creatures in the area, and a Reflex save can be made to halve the damage.<br><br>A Small dragon has the listed Perform Requirements, Close Range, its Area is a 5 ft square, its Cost is 6 and it deals 3d6+1 earth damage.<br><br>A Medium dragon increases the Perform Requirements by 1, has Medium Range, its Area is a 10 ft square, its Cost is 10 and it deals 6d6+3 earth damage.<br><br>A Large dragon increases the Perform Requirements by 3, has Long range, its Area is a 15 ft square, its Cost is 13 and it deals 9d6+5 earth damage.</p>\n\n\n\n",
